想三國誌依個名<br />\n<br />\n第四集好多人讚，但我真係唔鐘意，夾硬玩埋佢，真係太gay,同埋唔鐘意武器係筆同琴，不過依d 係我自己個人喜惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fa8d513eac580482ac772a9bf36e70a6730853","tid":56399,"uid":17286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T04:56:11.000Z","msg":"今集一男一女主角<br />\n終於唔係hehe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然hehe又真係好感動"},{"pid":"570766f26a346e786991fc70439c131d32c27cea","tid":56399,"uid":9382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:51:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今集一男一女主角<br />\n終於唔係hehe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然hehe又真係好感動</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得一次hehe姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw個畫風好似仲衰過以前"}]}